14:48.455 --> 14:51.022
I think there's been
a misunderstanding.

14:51.024 --> 14:52.924
Oh, look at that, you're
right next to a big trash can.

14:52.926 --> 14:54.092
You ever watch cartoons?

14:56.229 --> 14:57.362
Adam?

14:57.364 --> 14:58.596
W-What are you doing here?

14:58.598 --> 15:00.231
I'm just letting this guy know

15:00.233 --> 15:02.100
