15:22.122 --> 15:23.187
...but that was a--

15:23.189 --> 15:25.123
a slight exaggeration

15:25.125 --> 15:27.158
in-in the sense that, um,

15:27.160 --> 15:30.128
h-he never did anything
like that, ever.

15:30.130 --> 15:33.298
Where's the funny part
to that story?

15:33.300 --> 15:35.300
Oh, well, um,
the funny part is,

15:35.302 --> 15:37.402
