Bob Thompson.

15:38.371 --> 15:40.305
That is funny.

15:40.307 --> 15:42.006
(laughing)

15:42.008 --> 15:44.242
(laughing):
Well, that is funny.

15:45.145 --> 15:46.210
And I hope that one day,

15:46.212 --> 15:47.312
