16:21.014 --> 16:22.714
Didn't care?

16:22.716 --> 16:24.248
Well, I cared a lot!

16:24.250 --> 16:25.450
I was going crazy!

16:25.452 --> 16:27.185
Well, why didn't you
say something?

16:27.187 --> 16:30.321
Because you hate it
when I get jealous.

16:30.323 --> 16:32.090
Well, I hated it when
we were in our 20s

16:32.092 --> 16:33.725
and guys were hitting on me
all the time.

16:33.727 --> 16:35.193
Guys were hitting on you
all the time?

16:35.195 --> 16:36.394
Who were these guys?
Are they tall?

16:36.396 --> 16:38.196
See,

16:38.198 --> 16:39.430
that's what I was looking for.

16:39.432 --> 16:40.999
What?

16:41.001 --> 16:44.168
Well, a little jealousy is nice.

16:45.171 --> 16:47.305
Wha-- since when?

16:47.307 --> 16:50.341
Apparently, the older I get,
the more I'm gonna need.

16:50.343 --> 16:53.378
Good...

16:53.380 --> 16:55.046
'cause I am tired of pretending

16:55.048 --> 16:56.414
