17:34.521 --> 17:36.421
And, uh, the word "salami."

17:36.423 --> 17:38.156
So, there might be
some fallout from that.

17:38.158 --> 17:39.824
But, uh, okay, here we go.

17:49.335 --> 17:51.235
So, after all of this,

17:51.237 --> 17:53.604
we have decided to be completely
honest with each other.

17:53.606 --> 17:55.807
That's right,
no more secrets.
Mm.

17:55.809 --> 17:57.742
I like that, Don.
We should do that, too.

17:57.744 --> 17:59.710
Hey, I'm way ahead
of you, baby.

17:59.712 --> 18:01.846
That's why I told you
about Adam's secret boat.

18:05.785 --> 18:07.351
